[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">(8:23)<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">wish</st> that my <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> were a well full of <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and my <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> were a <st data-num=\"04726\" class=\"\">fountain</st> full of <st data-num=\"01832\" class=\"\">tears</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">If they were, I could <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">cry</st> <st data-num=\"03119\" class=\"\">day</st> and <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"02491\" class=\"\">those</st> of my <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">dear</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"02491\" class=\"\">who have been killed</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">(9:1) <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">wish</st> I had a <st data-num=\"04411\" class=\"\">lodging place</st> in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st><p class=\"poetry\">where I could spend some time like a weary <st data-num=\"0732\" class=\"\">traveler</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Then I would <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">desert</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walk away</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">from</st> them<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they are <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"05003\" class=\"\">unfaithful</st> to God,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"06116\" class=\"\">congregation</st><n id=\"2\" /> of people that has <st data-num=\"0898\" class=\"\">been disloyal</st> to him.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThese people are like soldiers who have <st data-num=\"01869\" class=\"\">readied</st> their <st data-num=\"07198\" class=\"\">bows</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">tongues</st> are always ready to shoot out <st data-num=\"08267\" class=\"\">lies</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They have <st data-num=\"01396\" class=\"\">become powerful</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">but they have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> done so by <st data-num=\"0530\" class=\"\">honest means</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, they <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">do</st> one <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil thing</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">after</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">another</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">pay attention to</st> me.<n id=\"5\" /></p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">Everyone</st> must <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">be on</st> his <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">guard</st> around his <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">friends</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He must <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> even <st data-num=\"05921 0982\">trust</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">any</st> of his <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">relatives</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">one of them</st> will <st data-num=\"06117\" class=\"\">find some way</st> <st data-num=\"06117\" class=\"\">to cheat</st> him.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">And <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> his <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">friends</st> will <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">tell</st> <st data-num=\"07400\" class=\"\">lies</st> about him.</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">One friend</st> <st data-num=\"02048\" class=\"\">deceives</st> <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">another</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">tells</st> the <st data-num=\"0571\" class=\"\">truth</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">These people have <st data-num=\"03925\" class=\"\">trained</st> <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">themselves</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">tell</st> <st data-num=\"08267\" class=\"\">lies</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"05753\" class=\"\">do wrong</st> and <st data-num=\"03811\" class=\"\">are unable</st> to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">repent</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They do one <st data-num=\"08496\" class=\"\">act of violence</st> after <st data-num=\"08496\" class=\"\">another</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and one <st data-num=\"04820\" class=\"\">deceitful thing</st> after <st data-num=\"04820\" class=\"\">another</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"03985\" class=\"\">refuse</st> to <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">pay attention</st> to me,\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">Therefore</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of Heaven\u2019s Armies <st data-num=\"0559\">says</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">now</st> <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">purify</st> them in the fires of affliction<n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"0974\" class=\"\">test</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wickedness</st> of my <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">dear</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"3\" /> has <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">left</st> me <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">no choice</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">What</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">else</st> can I <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st>?<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">tongues</st> are like <st data-num=\"07819\" class=\"\">deadly</st> <st data-num=\"02671\" class=\"\">arrows</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They are always <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">telling</st> <st data-num=\"04820\" class=\"\">lies</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">Friendly words</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">for</st> their <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">neighbors</st> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">come</st> from their <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouths</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but their <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">minds</st> are <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">thinking up</st> <st data-num=\"0696\" class=\"\">ways to trap</st> them.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">punish</st> them <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> doing <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">such things</st>!\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"0518 03808\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"05358\" class=\"\">bring retribution</st> on <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">such</st> a <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> as <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st>!\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"05375 01065\">weep</st> and <st data-num=\"05375 05092\">mourn</st><n id=\"2\" /> for the grasslands <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will sing a <st data-num=\"07015\" class=\"\">mournful song</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"04999\" class=\"\">pastures</st> in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they are so <st data-num=\"03341\" class=\"\">scorched</st> <st data-num=\"01097\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">travels through</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of <st data-num=\"04735\" class=\"\">livestock</st> is <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no longer</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> there.<p class=\"poetry\">Even the <st data-num=\"05775\" class=\"\">birds</st> in the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"0929\" class=\"\">wild animals</st> in the fields<p class=\"poetry\">have <st data-num=\"05074\" class=\"\">fled</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">are gone</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"2\" /> a <st data-num=\"01530\" class=\"\">heap of ruins</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08577\" class=\"\">Jackals</st> will make their <st data-num=\"04583\" class=\"\">home</st> there.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05414 08077\">destroy</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st><p class=\"poetry\">so that <st data-num=\"01097\" class=\"\">no</st> one will be able to <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in them.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> is <st data-num=\"0376 02450\">wise</st> enough to <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understand</st> why <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> has happened?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"01696 0413\">has</st> a <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">word</st> from the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> that can <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">explain</st> it?<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 04100\">Why</st> does the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">lie in ruins</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Why is it as <st data-num=\"03341\" class=\"\">scorched</st> as a <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">desert</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">through</st> which <st data-num=\"01097\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">travels</st>?\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">answered</st>, \u201cThis has happened <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because</st> these people have <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">rejected</st> my <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">laws</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> I <st data-num=\"05414 06440\">gave</st> them. They have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">obeyed</st> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">me</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">followed</st> those laws.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "Instead they have <st data-num=\"01980 0310\">followed</st> the <st data-num=\"08307\" class=\"\">stubborn inclinations</st> of their own <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">hearts</st>. They have <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">paid allegiance to</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"01168\" class=\"\">gods called Baal</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> their <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">fathers</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03925\" class=\"\">taught</st> them to do.",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So then</st>, listen to <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">what</st> I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>, the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">I</st> will make <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> the <st data-num=\"03939\" class=\"\">bitter food</st> of suffering and <st data-num=\"08248\" class=\"\">drink</st> the <st data-num=\"07219\" class=\"\">poison</st> <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> of judgment.<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "I will <st data-num=\"06327\" class=\"\">scatter</st> them among <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">neither</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">they</st> nor their <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st><n id=\"1\" /> have <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">known</st> anything <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">about</st>. I will <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st> people chasing <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">after</st> them with <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">swords</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> I have <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> them.\u2019\u201d<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st><n id=\"1\" /> told me to <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">say</st> to this people:<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">Take note</st> of what I say.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07121 0935\">Call</st> for the <st data-num=\"06969\" class=\"\">women who mourn for the dead</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0413 07971 0935\">Summon</st> those who are the most <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">skilled</st> at it!\u201d<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I said, \u201cIndeed,<n id=\"1\" /> let them <st data-num=\"04116\" class=\"\">come quickly</st> and <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">sing</st> a <st data-num=\"05092\" class=\"\">song of mourning</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> us.<p class=\"poetry\">Let them wail loudly until <st data-num=\"01832\" class=\"\">tears</st> <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">stream from</st> our own <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st><p class=\"poetry\">and our <st data-num=\"06079\" class=\"\">eyelids</st> <st data-num=\"05140\" class=\"\">overflow</st> with <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of <st data-num=\"05092\" class=\"\">wailing</st> is soon to be <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> in <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018We <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">are</st> <st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">utterly</st> <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">ruined</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> We <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">are</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">completely</st> <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">disgraced</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> we have <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">left</st> our <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> our <st data-num=\"04908\" class=\"\">houses</st> have been <st data-num=\"07993\" class=\"\">torn down!</st>\u2019\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">So now</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> you wailing <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">women</st>, <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">Open</st> your <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">ears</st> to the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> from his <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03925\" class=\"\">Teach</st> your <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughters</st> this <st data-num=\"05092\" class=\"\">mournful song</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and let every <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">woman</st> teach her <st data-num=\"07468\" class=\"\">neighbor</st> this <st data-num=\"07015\" class=\"\">lament</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">Death</st> has <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">climbed in</st><n id=\"1\" /> through our <st data-num=\"02474\" class=\"\">windows</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It has <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">entered</st> into our <st data-num=\"0759\" class=\"\">fortified houses</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It has <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">taken away</st> our <st data-num=\"05768\" class=\"\">children</st> who play in the <st data-num=\"02351\" class=\"\">streets</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It has taken away our <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st> who gather in the <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">city squares</st>.\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01696\">Tell</st> your daughters and neighbors, \u2018The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 05002\">says</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThe <st data-num=\"05038\" class=\"\">dead bodies</st> of <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">people</st> will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">lie</st> scattered everywhere<p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"01828\" class=\"\">manure</st> scattered <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"06440 07704\">a field</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will lie scattered on the ground <p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"05995\" class=\"\">grain</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">that has been</st> <st data-num=\"07114\" class=\"\">cut down</st> but has <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">not</st> been <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">gathered</st>.\u201d\u2019\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><n id=\"1\" /> The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">says</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">Wise people</st> should <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">boast</st> that <st data-num=\"02451\" class=\"\">they are wise</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">Powerful people</st> should <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">boast</st> that <st data-num=\"01369\" class=\"\">they are powerful</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06223\" class=\"\">Rich people</st> should <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">boast</st> that <st data-num=\"06239\" class=\"\">they are rich</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588 0518\">If</st> people want to <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">boast</st>, they should <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">boast</st> about <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">They should boast that they <st data-num=\"07919\" class=\"\">understand</st> and <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\">They should boast that they know and understand<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"06213\">act out of</st> <st data-num=\"02617\" class=\"\">faithfulness</st>, <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">fairness</st>, and <st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">justice</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> I <st data-num=\"02654\" class=\"\">desire</st> people to do <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these things</st>,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Watch out</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> is soon <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st> when I will <st data-num=\"06485 05921\">punish</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> those who are <st data-num=\"04135\" class=\"\">circumcised</st> only in the <st data-num=\"06190\" class=\"\">flesh</st>.<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "That is, I will <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">punish</st> the <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egyptians</st>, the <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judeans</st>, the <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edomites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 05983\">Ammonites</st>, the <st data-num=\"04124\" class=\"\">Moabites</st>, and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">desert</st> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">people</st> who <st data-num=\"07112\" class=\"\">cut</st> their <st data-num=\"07112\" class=\"\">hair short</st> at the <st data-num=\"06285\" class=\"\">temples</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> I will do so <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">none</st> of the people of those <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> are really <st data-num=\"06189\" class=\"\">circumcised</st> in the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span>\u2019s sight.<n id=\"2\" /> Moreover, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">none</st> of the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st><n id=\"3\" /> are <st data-num=\"06189\" class=\"\">circumcised</st> when it comes to their <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">hearts</st>.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  }
]